      "tool_name": "classroom_tagger",
      "description": "Interactive tap-to-tag classroom scavenger hunt. Student taps objects, picks their material from a 6-option palette, gets green tick on correct or a contextual hint on wrong answer. Summary strip tracks tagged count and distinct materials discovered.",
